TI  - Combining household surveys and interviews to understand irrigation technology adoption among farmers in Maharashtra (India)
T2  - FRONTIERS IN WATER
LA  - English
KW  - farmers
KW  - irrigation adoption
KW  - behavioral psychology
KW  - RANAS behavioral model
KW  - SSBC behavioral model
