TI  - Local perceptions of the conversion of cropland to forestland program in Jiangxi, Shaanxi, and Sichuan, China
T2  - JOURNAL OF FORESTRY RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Forest policy
KW  - Ecological restoration
KW  - Local perception
