TI  - Integrated techno-economic and life cycle assessment of shared circular business model based blockchain-enabled dynamic grapevoltaic farm for major grape growing states in India
T2  - RENEWABLE ENERGY
LA  - English
KW  - Dynamic agrivoltaics
