TI  - The Potential Role of Precision Agriculture in Building Sustainable Livelihoods and Farm Resilience Amid Climate Change: A Stakeholders' Perspective from Southern Punjab, Pakistan
T2  - LAND
LA  - English
KW  - future agricultural technologies
