TI  - A sudden and widespread change in symptoms and incidence of vascular streak dieback of cocoa (Theobroma cacao) linked to environmental change in Sulawesi, Indonesia
T2  - AGRICULTURE ECOSYSTEMS & ENVIRONMENT
