TI  - Profiling and Prioritizing Climate-Smart Aquaculture Technologies, Innovations, and Management Practices in Kenya
T2  - AQUACULTURE RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - aquaculture
KW  - climate-smart agriculture
KW  - CSA pillars
