TI  - Exploring adaptive capacity at the land-sea interface: insights from coastal rural communities in Chile
T2  - ECOLOGY AND SOCIETY
LA  - English
KW  - coastal communities
KW  - fishers' responses
KW  - hypothetical scenarios
