TI  - Designing low-input upland rice-based cropping systems with conservation agriculture for climate change adaptation: A six-year experiment in M'b'e, Bouake, Cote d'Ivoire
T2  - FIELD CROPS RESEARCH
LA  - English
KW  - Conservation agriculture (CA)
KW  - Transition
KW  - Risk
