TI  - Green development in agriculture: technology-driven solutions to boost soybean productivity on tidal lands in Jambi, Indonesia
T2  - FRONTIERS IN AGRONOMY
LA  - English
KW  - economic feasibility
KW  - green development
KW  - integrated crop management
