TI  - Resilience of conservation agriculture vs conventional agriculture in durum-wheat farming: a Tunisian semi-arid case study
T2  - EURO-MEDITERRANEAN JOURNAL FOR ENVIRONMENTAL INTEGRATION
LA  - English
KW  - Climate action
KW  - Conservation agriculture
KW  - Durum-wheat
KW  - Resilience
