TI  - Estimating the Potential Economic Value of Seasonal Forecasts in West Africa: A Long-Term Ex-Ante Assessment in Senegal
T2  - WEATHER CLIMATE AND SOCIETY
LA  - English
KW  - CLIMATE PREDICTION
KW  - SAHEL RAINFALL
KW  - BURKINA-FASO
