TI  - Farmers' indigenous knowledge of tree conservation and acidic soil amendments: The role of "baabbo" and "Mona" systems: Lessons from Gedeo community, Southern Ethiopia
T2  - COGENT FOOD & AGRICULTURE
LA  - English
KW  - Indigenous knowledge system
