TI  - The multifaceted meaning of drought: perspectives from Durango's agricultural stakeholders
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL RESEARCH-CLIMATE
LA  - English
KW  - droughts
KW  - water
KW  - agriculture
KW  - climate change
KW  - IMPACTS
