TI  - The Impact of Heavy Rainfall Variability on Fertilizer Application Rates: Evidence from Maize Farmers in China
T2  - INTERNATIONAL JOURNAL OF ENVIRONMENTAL RESEARCH AND PUBLIC HEALTH
