TI  - Capacity Building Approach and Application: Utilization of Earth Observation Data and Geospatial Information Technology in the Hindu Kush Himalaya
T2  - FRONTIERS IN ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE
LA  - English
KW  - capacity building
KW  - informal education
KW  - SME
KW  - SERVIR
