TI  - Assessing and managing risks to strengthen the resilience of surface water delivery systems under drought in irrigation districts
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL SCIENCE & POLICY
LA  - English
KW  - Spatial risk assessment
KW  - SOP failure
KW  - Hydraulic-operational simulation
KW  - Irrigation district resilience
