TI  - Resource mapping amid climate crisis for protection of hunter gatherer community livelihoods in Northern Tanzania
T2  - FRONTIERS IN CLIMATE
LA  - English
KW  - resource mapping
KW  - hunter-gatherer livelihoods
KW  - climate change impact
