TI  - The synergetic effect of drought and land use changes on Ethiopian Rift Valley Northwestern Escarpment livelihood systems
T2  - DISCOVER ENVIRONMENT
LA  - English
KW  - Climate variability
KW  - Drought
KW  - LULCC
