TI  - Conservation agriculture improves adaptive capacity of cropping systems to climate stress in Malawi
T2  - AGRICULTURAL SYSTEMS
LA  - English
KW  - Heat stress
KW  - Intercropping
KW  - Maize
KW  - Malawi
KW  - No tillage
KW  - Rotation
