TI  - Beyond Fixed Dates and Coarse Resolution: Developing a Dynamic Dry Season Crop Calendar for Paddy in Indonesia from 2001 to 2021
T2  - AGRONOMY-BASEL
LA  - English
KW  - crop calendar
