TI  - Assessment of the flood vulnerability of shrimp farms using a multicriteria evaluation and GIS: a case study in the Bangpakong Sub-Basin, Thailand
T2  - ENVIRONMENTAL EARTH SCIENCES
LA  - English
KW  - Flood
