TI  - Evaluating sustainable adaptation strategies for vulnerable mega-deltas using system dynamics modelling: Rice agriculture in the Mekong Delta's An Giang Province, Vietnam
T2  - SCIENCE OF THE TOTAL ENVIRONMENT
